      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW XANTIPPE (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (27.94) in a Special conditions H at Horsham. Has a strong winning record here. Can make amends. MOTORSPORT (1) ran below best last time finishing eighth (31.10) over 525m at this track from Box 6. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Cannot be taken lightly. IVORY MIHARA (2) was favourite last start and led all the way, scoring by one length (30.55) at this track in a Grade 5 over 525m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from six starts. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. MEANINGFUL (4) has strong credentials over this journey.",
